Package: geneviewer
Type: Package
Title: Gene Cluster Visualizations in R
Version: 0.1.6
Author: Niels van der Velden
Maintainer: Niels van der Velden <n.s.j.vandervelden@gmail.com>
Description: 'geneviewer' is an R package designed to plot gene clusters. 
             It can import data directly from GenBank files, perform BlastP 
             alignments and visualize the results in gene arrow maps. In addition 
             there are extensive options for customization such as addition of 
             alegend, labels, annotations, customized scales, colors, tooltips 
             and much more.
